title: How to Draw: Dogs and Puppies
creator: Draw Animals and Pets Studio

extendedInfo.description: Always wanted to Learn some drawing techniques, in order to be able to put on paper, what i've seen in real life. With the help of this application, you'll draw anything in no time. Basically these are step-by-step tutorials for drawing dogs and puppies, you are pretty familiar with.Try yourself or teach your kid.Each drawing divided in 5 to 15 steps, and its easy to follow.Have fun with this lessons at home, in school, on paper, chalk on asphalt - do it everywhere!*** 26 dogs and puppies drawing tutorials ***In our application you will find lessons that will teach you how to draw: - How to draw Scooby Doo - How to draw Snoopy - How to draw Brian Griffin - How to draw Pluto - How to draw Courage - How to draw Santa's Little Helper from Simpsons - How to draw Mutley - How to draw Odie - How to draw Underdog - How to draw Goofy - How to draw Ninetales Pokemon - How to draw Entei Pokemon - How to draw Spike and Tyke - How to draw Puppy Labrador Retriever - How to draw Puppy German Shepherd - How to draw Dachshund - How to draw Cocker Spaniel - How to draw Pug Laughing - How to draw Husky face - How to draw Boxer Dog - How to draw Cute Pit Bull - How to draw Yorkshire Terrier - How to draw Shih Tzu Dog - How to draw Puppy & Kitty - How to draw CatDogDrawing is fun, but traditionally not so fun to learn. Unless you can afford a private tutor, you usually have to take a class that requires you to adhere to a specific schedule.  The How to Draw: Dogs and Puppies app makes learning to draw as easy and as flexible as possible. All you need to provide is time, medium, and environment in which you want to draw!The How to Draw: Dogs and Puppies app makes learning to draw a snap by using mimicking, a method of drawing that is ideal for both beginners and advanced artists. Simply follow the step-by-step instructions. You will learn to draw in no time!*** FEATURES ***The following is a list of the features that you can expect with the How to Draw: Dogs and Puppies app:- Free to use!- Portable so you can learn to draw wherever you take your mobile device!- One of the largest collections of tutorials for drawing celebrities in a single app!- Easy to follow step-by-step instructions for each tutorial!- Each tutorial associated with a rating so you can choose according to your drawing level!- Navigation controls that allow you to learn at your own pace!Try How to Draw: Dogs and Puppies app today!Short review of Cartoon dogs you will draw in our application:- Scooby-Doo - jovial and fun-loving, and just human enough to be understood, Scooby-Doo is by nature a chicken-heart. When pressed, however, he always comes through with a sense of whimsical bravery. - Brian Griffin is an 8-year old talking white Labrador who has lived with the Griffin family since Peter picked him up as a stray. - Clifford greets each day with optimism because he knows something exciting is bound to happen! He doesn't have to be asked twice to explore Birdwell Island with his dog pals, Cleo and T-Bone, or with his favorite human in the whole wide world, Emily Elizabeth. Clifford is a kid at heart. He may be big and red, but as far as he's concerned, he's just like any other dog. - .. and many more!
